\SE[11] How are you, Unagi-chan...? \SE[6] Do you think Luna
can be saved...?

\SE[2] Maybe... I think it'll be fine. \!\SE[3] Using the
same method as Meria-chan...

\SE[2]Well, that's not a problem, right? \SE[3]What seems
more dangerous is...

\SE[90]Alice... Well, without a doubt, she will definitely
interfere. \SE[91]

\SE[3]It's okay...! We've also become stronger than
before...! \SE[1]I'm sure we'll manage somehow!

\SE[74]Well, there's no point in worrying now that we've
come this far...

\SE[2]It's not really a problem... but... \!\SE[4]Can I ask
everyone for one favor?

\SE[3]Tell me anything...! I'm full of motivation, so I'll
do my best!

\SE[4]When entering the world of dreams, I borrow the power
of the magic items... \!\SE[3]But I ran out of Meria-chan's
share.

\SE[2]I have them made by the magician.... \SE[3]They're a
bit unusual.... \SE[2]I don't live in the town.

I kind of thought it would be nice to live a peaceful life
like this.

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen.
However, I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.
